lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super lazyTrees.Item>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lazyTrees.LazySearchTree<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class LazySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super lazyTrees.Item>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    The Class LazySearchTree stores Items in a BST, and performs lazy deletions of Items. It prints both lazy deleted and non lazy deleted. The find max and min methods considering only the lazy deleted Items.
    Author:
    pavlosp1967
